{"tid":2258661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益系列］唔想室友女朋友上黎可以點做","createTime":"2020-10-26T08:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T16:19:28.000Z","uid":217650,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"36b4fde8c831915433388e43a1b122f0cb964014","tid":2258661,"uid":217650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:23:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n因為小弟同屋企人出現分歧相處得唔開心<br />\n所以自己同個朋友出黎夾份租屋<br />\n咁個陣入伙前佢就話佢條女一星期會上黎訓一晚<br />\n但事實呢 佢條女一星期最少會上黎四晚<br />\n次次上黎就好似自己屋企咁款 開行哂啲冷氣<br />\n衫褲雜物亂咁放哂係廳 <br />\n半夜三更係廳開到喇叭大大聲咁睇啲大陸劇集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早兩日諗住無嘢做 室友話今晚唔返<br />\n今次仲唔到我獨享成間屋做霸主<br />\n所以諗住冷手打個熱飛機梳乎下<br />\n正當我左青龍 右滑鼠 去到高潮之際<br />\n度門突然間打開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來條女有間屋既鎖匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當刻我真係又尷尬 又憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家下連係自己屋企打個飛機都好似我唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後大家都當無事 返入自己房 咁我就當無事啦<br />\n點知今日個室友同我講：「下次啲私人野返入房做呀嘛 費事大家尷尬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n唔講猶至可 一講就把幾火 咁我地個屋苑就要拍八達通（住戶證）先到黎既<br />\n我一直都以為係我室友帶條女上黎<br />\n點知原來條女係有住戶證 有鎖匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明兩個人平分租金燈油火蠟<br />\n仲要搞到我成日好似寄人籬下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家先住咗半年 有咩方法可以奪回主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6216ead42781aa0efd845a150a34f7d4c06d0766","tid":2258661,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"搵第2個室友"},{"pid":"273479395c77038f24e3bb9fb11fb42b0510b6ab","tid":2258661,"uid":357936,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:26:48.000Z","msg":"照係佢面前打飛機，唔好理，想打就打。<br />\n好快佢以後唔上黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaa52da65d209fbf999ebb585196ec9c3476fb3","tid":2258661,"uid":351453,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講啦<br />\n一係夾多分份錢條女比 條女冇份夾租既話<br />\n有乜理由條仔唔係度條女都照有哂野自己上黎<br />\n<br />\n仲要睇大陸劇真係叫佢食屎啦"},{"pid":"bcd136e3ab107483b6dd720815bfe3ec460c55fc","tid":2258661,"uid":302390,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"帶多幾條仔上嚟住話係自己男朋友"},{"pid":"c2a5565afadce48a3ee5783e8b85ee22184fe2d9","tid":2258661,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"條女用晒水費電費 有一半係你畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99cba34b885392b38372c1939343d86466552bd7","tid":2258661,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:28:15.000Z","msg":"中出你fd"},{"pid":"6ee442a393a1b98c231b43e36dc90502fa0cf2fa","tid":2258661,"uid":245484,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"直接問你個FD<br />\n條女係咪可以齊齊砌? 點解要幫你養埋你條女? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065ac45162e6e7fbdb640f249e5f559facbb726e","tid":2258661,"uid":31001,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講當初傾既時候唔係咁<br />\n同佢講唔想佢條女成日上黎"},{"pid":"97a295e1bc73f29b51c35ae58f9c21fa8861b2e2","tid":2258661,"uid":7125,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"一係就份租除三<br />\n<br />\n一係就你都帶條女 要惡過佢<br />\n<br />\n以暴易暴"},{"pid":"bc379f2f779e57108c16a3012cb0cf187be50e28","tid":2258661,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:53:39.000Z","msg":"我諗最主要係佢地冇尊重你姐，錢都係次要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇你同室友本身感情如何囉，攤牌唔掂都要搬啦"},{"pid":"42d54c47690b912c1ce8f67ecb95622cafd3ba4e","tid":225866